，冇人評稅&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n冇評稅=唔使交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64081fd41dca46fc224b1443e927e884d2be0de","tid":1419261,"uid":276954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30da92c6d421ffff110518dcdacb861ba7a50c18","tid":1419261,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79fd509244f96cd758520bf1b7cf415d0bf92791","tid":1419261,"uid":276954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"我唔交稅住...<br />\n<br />\n唔交稅點可能?遲交都要加多5%。<br />\n<br />\n但你嘅評稅1日未完成,政府都唔可以開張稅單嚟收稅。<br />\n<br />\n打電話通知收唔到報稅單。拖一拖。<br />\n<br />\n張報稅表未簽名佢都唔可以開始。<br />\n<br />\n一於拖得就拖。吹呀!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話，如果稅務大樓被破壞（例如打風，或者其他原因&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），咁稅務局咪暫時冇人返工，冇人評稅&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n冇評稅=唔使交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"佢唔會預咁多人玩<br />\nJust play with them (我估有人會合作同你玩)"}]}